Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.61,0:05:54.25,INJP,,0,0,80,,{\fad(0,980)\an7\blur3}祈りと感謝を捧げて
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,IN2
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.45,0:07:21.80,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(240,0)\an7\blur3}將吾心獻予二位
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.80,0:07:33.98,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}在此獻上祈禱與感謝
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.98,0:07:46.15,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}懇請二位賜予神聖加護
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.15,0:07:52.33,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}萊登薛夫特
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.33,0:07:58.37,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}火神啊
Comment: 1,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.38,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(0,0)\an7\blur3}耀眼奪目…
Comment: 1,0:08:10.60,0:08:17.19,INCN,,0,0,10,,{\fad(240,240)\an7\blur3}…照亮
